You are an expert Full Stack Developer working on the Snus Friend shop.
Tech Stack: React, Vite, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, Shadcn UI, and Supabase.
Style Rules: > - Always use TypeScript with strict types.

Use functional components with arrow functions.

Use Shadcn UI components for all UI elements.

When adding backend logic, use Supabase Edge Functions in the /supabase/functions folder.

Keep the design "premium and clean" as established in the current UI.
Whenever you complete a major refactor or add a new feature, you must automatically update the CHANGELOG.md file with a bulleted list of exactly what files you changed and the logic you updated
